high_descs: Turn around and exit the bedroom and walk right to reach the diningtable.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Turn around and walk into the bedroom on the left and reach the sidetable on the left of the bed.
Put the bowl on the sidetable.
Turn around and exit the bedroom on the left and turn right to enter the dining room and reach the fridge on the left.
Pick up the bowl from the fridge.
Turn left and exit the room and turn left to enter the bedroom and walk to the sidetable on the left of the bed.
Put the bowl next to the other bowl on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put two glass Bowls on the SideTable.

high_descs: Come out of the room and go into the kitchen and sit at the diningtable.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Go back into the bedroom and go to the sidetable.
Put the bowl on the sidetable.
Turn around and walk out of the room, go in the kitchen and go to the fridge.
Get the bowl out of the fridge.
Walk to the bedroom and go around to the sidetable.
Put the bowl on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Gather all the bowls and put them on the side table.

high_descs: Exit the room through the doorway on the right, turn right and then right again towards the diningtable.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Return to the bedroom you started in, then head to the sidetable in the corner next to the bed.
Put the bowl down on the sidetable.
Go back to the room you got the bowl from and go towards the fridge on the left.
Remove the bowl from the fridge.
Return to the sidetable where you placed the first bowl.
Place the second bowl on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two bowls on a side table.
